ith stale in-memory data containing phantom `1-1-foo` and reverted stories 16-5 through 16-8\n- **Session cost**: ~$2.63 incremental ($677.17 cumulative), pure waste\n- **Cumulative waste estimate**: $73-90 (11-13% of total budget) from no-ops, phantoms, and state corruption\n- **The fix is to stop ralph.** Not fix the JSON. Not add guards. Just kill the process. This has been the answer since session 31 and 6 action items have been carried forward unresolved across 4 sessions."}],"totalDurationMs":90433,"totalTokens":26746,"totalToolUseCount":9,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2475,"cache_read_input_tokens":24025,"output_tokens":245,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2475},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
